dct_title_s: Tasmania 1:250 000 series / produced by TASMAP, Location Services, Department of Primary Industries, Parks, Water and Environment.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, hypsometric tints, shading, and spot heights. Insets: King Island -- Macquarie Island. Topographic map series of Tasmania covering the whole state. Includes index to adjoining sheets, and location map. "Grid lines are 10 000 meters intervals of the Map Grid of Australia 1994 (MGA94) Zone 55."
